{"tid":922900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戀上賤男 癡心ol買波子","createTime":"2018-11-30T18:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T02:54:00.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9ed7d885fe640d68e6749dd3463810bad027aaf6","tid":922900,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WLdXaAT11n8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWLdXaAT11n8&d=%2FrJA25CgA%2BBTVbOoZHtMgEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ef3f7ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WLdXaAT11n8</a><br />\n【本報訊】妙齡律師行女文員疑慘遇情場騙子，拍拖僅半年，男友聲稱在上海遇意外、腳趾受重創入院，要她幫忙籌醫藥費。她向親友及財務公司借錢，甚至盜用律師樓客戶資料上會買名車，騙取財務公司 135 萬元貸款；但男友原來一直身在香港，每次遙控她將錢放入商場貯物櫃交收。她被騙近 10 個月，直至遇見男友駕名車穿梭街頭才恍然大悟自首。案件昨於區院開審。<br />\n記者：陳美珊"},{"pid":"e6be5f04c4bf7f09c220ed9a84a15e0c7a4f2842","tid":922900,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T18:10:28.000Z","msg":"個男人亂衝上的士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b5fc8cce06afd74870d32be2f4a57595c0cd63","tid":922900,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed7d885fe640d68e6749dd3463810bad027aaf6","tid":922900,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T18:09:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WLdXaAT11n8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWLdXaAT11n8&d=%2FrJA25CgA%2BBTVbOoZHtMgEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ef3f7ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WLdXaAT11n8</a><br />\n【本報訊】妙齡律師行女文員疑慘遇情場騙子，拍拖僅半年，男友聲稱在上海遇意外、腳趾受重創入院，要她幫忙籌醫藥費。她向親友及財務公司借錢，甚至盜用律師樓客戶資料上會買名車，騙取財務公司 135 萬元貸款；但男友原來一直身在香港，每次遙控她將錢放入商場貯物櫃交收。她被騙近 10 個月，直至遇見男友駕名車穿梭街頭才恍然大悟自首。案件昨於區院開審。<br />\n記者：陳美珊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"adb9e47ccbfd978ca30534943755b4f7a829cdb1","tid":922900,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15b5fc8cce06afd7